reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: After using this for a few weeks I went back and ordered a 2nd one. Sometimes I need it on both top and bottom racks to prevent things from flipping over. This is great for all the little cups and bowls my little kids use. I also use it over the Tupperware. Takes a little practice to find the best places to hook on to, but totally worth it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Plastic food containers and dish washers are a headache. This product has kept my containers from flipping over and fill with dirty water. Now if it could only dry them a bit more it would be spectacular.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars New favorite purchase
reviews.reviewText: Absolutely love this! Keeps all of my small and light items in place making it easier to clean the toddler items in the dish washer. Easy to clip on, my 3 year old likes to put it on and take it off when he’s helping with chores.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Holds small lids in the dishwasher
reviews.reviewText: This works well for small lids and other small items in the dishwasher. The only downside is the fact that it’s quite small and will only hold about two items depending on the size. Maybe like two cup lids. Other than that it’s a great item. Possibly you could get more than one if you need more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is an amazing product!Most of my pet dishes are plastic so this holds them in place.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for light plasticware
reviews.reviewText: This is my third one in about 8 years. They last as long as I expect. We use it at least once a day. They are fantastic for keeping small bowls from tipping over and filling with water. A must have.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Someone must’ve taken their motorcycle net and adapted it for the dishwasher to come up with this. It is a top rack game changer. All those little metal bowls that flip over and hold dirty water are tamed. Nothing goes flying. Give these as gifts to your friends with dishwashers. They will love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 30, 2022
reviews.reviewText: One of the clips broke off in the first few weeks of having this. We love the straps but this seems to be a constant problem with products like this.

This is fantastic for my husband and I ...who end up eating leftovers more than 1/2 the time, and have lots of small plastic containers and lids to wash in the dishwasher, and also baking utensils, measuring cups etc, this holds it all down for a great wash!! Love it!

reviews.reviewTitle: 搾乳機を食洗機で洗えるようになった！
reviews.reviewText: ベビー用品などを食洗機で洗うために購入。これと、小久保工業の食洗機用小物洗いバスケット（安いけど乳首固定できるし神アイテム）があれば哺乳瓶とか何でも食洗機でいけちゃいます！まじで神アイテムですので哺乳瓶、搾乳機を使っている方はぜひ！食洗機使うようになってから本当に自分の時間が増えました！あと、食洗機は80度洗いとか、ナノイーとかついて除菌できるタイプが絶対におすすめですよ！
Really good quality. Much better than other dish nets on the market, glad I bought two.
I have many small plastic containers and they always flip during washing. Some time I attach the hooks to the middle rung to prevent the smaller ones from flipping.
